{"tid":415172,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 關於申請日本apple id...","createTime":"2017-09-26T18:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T23:54:27.000Z","uid":80805,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f10b90d957b14c3c28e0d58f23bb6af5c5c7f7","tid":415172,"uid":80805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:18:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟今日買左部ip8<br />\n以前用開an機<br />\n諗住down番以前d game黎玩 就諗住申請番個日本acc<br />\n點知試哂網上嘅方法都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如itunes買免費app再申請 or響手機申請etc <br />\n到最後都俾我試到唔洗用信用卡嘅方法<br />\n當我打好哂資料 剩番最後一步電郵認證嘅時候&hellip;<br />\n就開始無限load+delete認證碼輪迴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問各位巴打有冇試過/其他辨法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb5031dd2b216c5d6b0841095bdf2976da2dcf8","tid":415172,"uid":141581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"我果陣開唔駛用信用卡 只係尻搵個日本地址就用到"},{"pid":"b1a02aab9d8816623bbc9c3deb25b41a61b3efbf","tid":415172,"uid":80805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:21:23.000Z","msg":"附上遺照<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/022009_1fd490fa130434a240d2f2aa1d0a084c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F022009_1fd490fa130434a240d2f2aa1d0a084c.jpg&h=a8791193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個跟住嘅下一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太驚嚇唔記得cap圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e95663f935cb0daf436c6a9d83085e45ce903e","tid":415172,"uid":80805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl